Definition: an oriental tobacco pipe with a long flexible tube connected to a container where the smoke is cooled by passing through water
Example: a bipolar world with the hookah and Turkish coffee versus hamburgers and Coca Cola
Synonyms: narghile, nargileh, sheesha, shisha, chicha, calean, kalian, water_pipe, hubble-bubble, hubbly-bubbly, pipe, an, oriental, tobacco, with, a, long, flexible, tube, connected, to, container, where, the, smoke, is, cooled, by, passing, through, water, bipolar, world, and, Turkish, coffee, versus, hamburgers, Coca, Cola
Category: noun.artifact
